(66411, 128435, 6531, 3, '南海路(demo 01)', '', '2013-08-28 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 1, 8, 'We''ve come nowhere\nHesitating and so we stroll\nAlong the path leading to fogs and shadows\nAnd so we walk and crawl with fear\n \nThe sky seems too grey \nColorless, no hope\nNostalgia occupies my mind\nI wonder it''s better we forget\n \nWe were to perspire\nBut we''ve never had a clue\nAbout here and everything that''s so unclear\nAnd about all these things we bear in mind\n \nThe grey sky above us\nHinds our vision and devour dreams\nWhat will become when we grow up\nIf we reach out what would we find within our palms\n\nThe sky seems too grey \nColorless, no hope\nNostalgia occupies my mind\nI wonder if it''s better we forget\n', '', 393, '', '阿仲', '瑪莉', '', '如何設計C++程式', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-08-28 00:42:51', '2015-03-12 14:01:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(66412, 128435, 6531, 2, '英雄電影(demo 01)', '', '2013-08-28 00:00:00', 2013, 19, 1, 7, '原本是和平的每一天\n原本只是個普通的少年\n但這一切突然全都改變\n\n邪惡勢力全部都出現\n挺身而出拯救了世界\n回到最初純淨的那一切\n\n故事情節瀰漫在腦中\n早就預測下一幕的發展\n人生情節是否也相同\n散場之後又如何\n\n和平的每一天     我過著和平的 和平的每一天\n只是個普通少年   我只是普通的 普通的少年\n無聊的每天耍廢   我只會無聊的 無聊的耍廢    \n正義的超級英雄   我不是正義的 也不是英雄\n\n平凡的人應該怎麼做 而不是坐在這裡 看著電影', '', 291, '', '阿仲', '阿仲', '', '如何設計C++程式', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-08-28 01:25:14', '2015-03-12 14:01:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
